    <section id="id6118544">
      <title>TO WRITE A DESCRIPTIVE PARAGRAPH / POEM</title>
      <section id="id4047758">
        <title>THIS IS A THINKING GAME!</title>
        <para id="id4827046">Who’s who ..... in the zoo? </para>
        <para id="id2087240">Can you work out the names of the animals in the four rhyming riddles below? </para>
        <para id="id2292723">They are all animals that can be seen in most zoos. Fill in each space. </para>
        <para id="id3434920">Tip: The answer to each riddle is given BUT the letters are not in the right order.</para>
        <section id="id4991898">
          <title>THE GREAT PRETENDER </title>
          <para id="id4613782">I am a creature that everyone fears: <emphasis effect="bold"/>Don’t trust my smile and don’t trust my tears.To think I’m asleep is a fatal mistake. This hungry - - - - - - - - - is wide awake!</para>
          <para id="id1373796">Answer:  clodeoric<emphasis effect="italics"/><emphasis effect="italics">  - </emphasis>MJB</para>
        </section>
      </section>
      <section id="id3604034">
        <title>SCAVENGER</title>
        <para id="id4870016">From shadows he watches the lions feast;hears the crunching of bone as they tear at a beast. When the lions have gone, he dines all aloneon dry clotted blood and splinters of bone.Friendless, detested, welcomed by noneHe’s the laughing - - - - - whom all creatures shun.</para>
        <para id="id6138061">Answer: heany<emphasis effect="italics"/><emphasis effect="italics"/>   - MJB</para>
        <section id="id4733567">
          <title>MR WONDERFUL</title>
          <para id="id3642044">I am the most beautiful cat of allI am a - - - - - from Bengal.</para>
          <para id="id4638463">Answer: grite - MJB</para>
        </section>
      </section>
      <section id="id5099854">
        <title>ZOO FAVOURITE</title>
        <para id="id3961991">I am the clown the kids love to see.I swing along from tree to tree.My arms are so long they reach to my knee I’m the friendliest, funniest young - - - - - - - - - -</para>
        <para id="id4330033">Answer: pincehmaze<emphasis effect="italics"> - </emphasis>MJB</para>
      </section>
